    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Boil</strong> a kettle</p>\r\n<p><strong>Slice</strong> the spring onions finely, discarding the root ends and keeping the green and white parts separate</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cut</strong> the mushrooms in half then slice finely</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cut</strong> the mangetout into bite-size pieces</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
