    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Peel</strong> the ginger (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Drain</strong> the tofu, pat dry with kitchen towel and cut into cubes</p>",
