    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> 1-2 tbsp vegetable oil to a large pot over a high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the ginger, chilli flakes (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), mushrooms and star anise and cook for 1 min, stirring constantly</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the shaoxing wine and cook for 1 min or until it evaporates, still stirring constantly</p>",
